Gold Extends Decline in London, Trading 1.8% Lower at $1,787.65 an Ounce

-- B y   S t u a r t   W a l l a c e
-- 
2011-09-15T13:06:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/gold-extends-decline-in-london-trading-1-8-lower-at-1-787-65-an-ounce.html
Gold extended its decline in
 London , trading 1.8 percent lower at $1,787.65 an ounce, after
the  European Central Bank  said it will lend euro-area banks
dollars in three separate three-month loans.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
